data.description:
Welcome to 64 Coventry Trail, a stunning residence nestled in the inviting Hearth Haven neighborhood of Wetumpka. This charming property for sale offers an exceptional living experience with its thoughtful design and high-quality finishes.
Step inside to discover a home that exudes warmth and elegance, featuring crown molding throughout, adding a touch of sophistication to every room. The wood-burning fireplace provides a cozy ambiance, perfect for gatherings or quiet evenings at home. Wood grain flooring seamlessly flows through the hallways, combining durability with the timeless appeal of hardwood.
The heart of this home is the kitchen, where granite countertops meet stainless steel appliances, complemented by a stylish tiled backsplash. Both bathrooms echo the kitchen's luxury with granite countertops and double vanities in the master bath, ensuring ample space for personal routines. The master bath also boasts a garden tub and separate shower, offering a spa-like retreat.
Each of the three bedrooms promises restful nights in serenely designed spaces. Meanwhile, energy efficiency is paramount with spray foam insulation and double pane windows, paired with a durable 30-year architectural shingle roof.
Outside, the covered back porch invites relaxation and entertainment in the privacy of your large backyard. 
64 Coventry Trail isn't just a house; it's a home waiting to be filled with new memories. Close to downtown Wetumpka for shopping and dining. Call me or your favorite realtor today for your private showing.
